<script> 
    (function() {
        function handleDataLayerUpdate(dataLayer) {
         // Get the latest event from the data layer (the last element in the array).
         var latestEvent = dataLayer[dataLayer.length - 1];

        // If the event is "gtm.load", "gtm.dom", or "gtm.scroll", use the second latest event instead.
        if (['gtm.load', 'gtm.dom', 'gtm.scroll'].includes(latestEvent.event) && dataLayer.length > 1) {
            latestEvent = dataLayer[dataLayer.length - 2];
        }
            // Get previously stored values from the session storage or set to an empty string if undefined.
            var creativeName = sessionStorage.getItem('creative_name') || "";
            var creativeSlot = sessionStorage.getItem('creative_slot') || "";
            var itemListName = sessionStorage.getItem('item_list_name') || "";
            var promotionName = sessionStorage.getItem('promotion_name') || "";
            var promotionId = sessionStorage.getItem('promotion_id') || "";

            // If the latest event is a 'select_promotion' event, update the session storage 
            // with the promotion name and creative slot if they are present in the event data.
            if (latestEvent.event === 'select_promotion') {
                if (latestEvent.ecommerce && latestEvent.ecommerce.promotion_name !== undefined) {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('promotion_name', latestEvent.ecommerce.promotion_name);
                }
                if (latestEvent.ecommerce && latestEvent.ecommerce.creative_slot !== undefined) {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('creative_slot', latestEvent.ecommerce.creative_slot);
                }
                if (latestEvent.ecommerce && latestEvent.ecommerce.promotion_id !== undefined) {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('promotion_id', latestEvent.ecommerce.promotion_id);
                }
                if (latestEvent.ecommerce && latestEvent.ecommerce.creative_name !== undefined) {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('creative_name', latestEvent.ecommerce.creative_name);
                }
            }
           
            // If the latest event is a 'select_item' event, update the session storage 
            // with the item list name if it is present in the event data.
            if (latestEvent.event === 'select_item') {
                if (latestEvent.ecommerce && latestEvent.ecommerce.item_list_name !== undefined) {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('item_list_name', latestEvent.ecommerce.item_list_name);
                }
            }
           
            // If the latest event is one of the listed e-commerce events, 
            // enrich the event data with the stored session data.
            if (['add_to_cart', 'remove_from_cart', 'add_to_wishlist', 'view_cart', 'begin_checkout', 'add_shipping_info', 'add_payment_info', 'purchase'].indexOf(latestEvent.event) !== -1) {
                // Create a new object to hold the enriched e-commerce data, starting with the existing data.
                var ecommerce = latestEvent.ecommerce || {};
                var items = ecommerce.items || [];
                // Map over the items array, creating a new array with the enriched data.
                items = items.map(function(item) {
                    // Create a new item object, using Object.assign to copy the existing item data.
                    var newItem = Object.assign({}, item);
                    // If the session storage contains values for promotion name, creative slot, and item list name, 
                    // add them to the new item object.
                    if (creativeName) newItem.promotion_name = promotionName;
                    if (creativeName) newItem.creative_name = creativeName;
                    if (creativeSlot) newItem.creative_slot = creativeSlot;
                    if (creativeSlot) newItem.promotion_slot = promotionId;
                    if (itemListName) newItem.item_list_name = itemListName;
                     // Return the new item object to be included in the new items array.
                    return newItem;
                });
                // Create a new object to hold the enriched e-commerce data.
                var enrichedEcommerceData = {
                    coupon: ecommerce.coupon,
                    currency: ecommerce.currency,
                    payment_type: ecommerce.payment_type,
                    shipping: ecommerce.shipping,
                    shipping_tier: ecommerce.shipping_tier,
                    tax: ecommerce.tax,
                    transaction_id: ecommerce.transaction_id,
                    value: ecommerce.value,
                    items: items,
                };
                // Push a new event to the data layer with the '_enriched' suffix 
                // and the enriched e-commerce data.
                dataLayer.push({
                    'event': latestEvent.event + '_enriched',
                    'ecommerce': enrichedEcommerceData
                });
            }

            // Clear all data from the session storage after a purchase event
            if (latestEvent.event === 'purchase') {
                sessionStorage.clear();
            }
        }

        // Ensure that the data layer array exists on the window object, creating it if necessary.
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        // Override the push method of the data layer array to include a call to the handleDataLayerUpdate function 
        // each time an item is pushed to the data layer.
        window.dataLayer.push = (function(pushOriginal) {
            return function() {
                pushOriginal.apply(window.dataLayer, arguments);
                handleDataLayerUpdate(window.dataLayer);
            };
        })(window.dataLayer.push);
    })();
</script>
